@startuml
title Регулировка температуры - Диаграмма последовательности

actor "Владелец дома" as User
participant "Мобильное приложение" as MobileApp
participant "API Gateway" as APIGateway
participant "API Controller" as APIController
participant "Command Handler" as CmdHandler
participant "Device Manager" as DevManager
participant "Device Registry" as DevRegistry
participant "MQTT Adapter" as MQTT
participant "Устройство отопления" as Heater
participant "Event Publisher" as EventPub
participant "БД Redis" as Redis
participant "Message Queue" as Kafka

User -> MobileApp: Передвигает ползунок температуры\n(установить 22°C)
MobileApp -> APIGateway: POST /api/heating/command\n{device_id: 123, temp: 22}
APIGateway -> APIController: Маршрутизация запроса

activate APIController
APIController -> APIController: Валидация входных данных
APIController -> CmdHandler: create_command(device_id, temp)

activate CmdHandler
CmdHandler -> DevRegistry: get_device_info(device_id)
activate DevRegistry
DevRegistry --> CmdHandler: DeviceInfo(тип, настройки)
deactivate DevRegistry

CmdHandler -> DevManager: get_current_state(device_id)
activate DevManager
DevManager -> Redis: get(device_id:state)
activate Redis
Redis --> DevManager: current_state(21°C, ON)
deactivate Redis
DevManager --> CmdHandler: current_state
deactivate DevManager

CmdHandler -> CmdHandler: validate_command()
CmdHandler -> MQTT: send_command(device_id, SET_TEMP, 22)

activate MQTT
MQTT -> Heater: MQTT: home/123/set_temp [22]
deactivate MQTT

Heater -> Heater: Устанавливает температуру
Heater -> MQTT: MQTT: home/123/telemetry [temp=22, status=ok]

activate MQTT
MQTT -> CmdHandler: on_command_ack(device_id, SUCCESS)
deactivate MQTT

CmdHandler -> DevManager: update_state(device_id, temp=22)
activate DevManager
DevManager -> Redis: set(device_id:state, temp=22)
activate Redis
Redis --> DevManager: OK
deactivate Redis
DevManager --> CmdHandler: state_updated
deactivate DevManager

CmdHandler -> EventPub: publish_event(device_id, TEMP_CHANGED, 22)

activate EventPub
EventPub -> Kafka: send(topic=heating-events, event)
deactivate EventPub

CmdHandler --> APIController: CommandResult(success, new_temp=22)
deactivate CmdHandler

APIController --> APIGateway: 200 OK {status: "updated", temp: 22}
APIGateway --> MobileApp: Response
MobileApp --> User: Отображает 22°C

@enduml